@kirillegrv First of, are you sure that this library is what you need? It is a digital identification tool for people with Swedish ID numbers.

Certificates are obtained by [signing an agreement with one of the banks selling BankID](https://www.bankid.com/en/om_bankid/bankid-in-my-services). 
One can test this package by using a [test certificate](https://www.bankid.com/assets/bankid/rp/FPTestcert2_20150818_102329.pfx) from [BankID:s developement pages](https://www.bankid.com/bankid-i-dina-tjanster/rp-info) (see [tests](https://github.com/hbldh/pybankid/blob/master/tests/test_client.py) and [test certificate obtaining code](https://github.com/hbldh/pybankid/blob/master/bankid/testcert.py)).

